  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 375f (190c).",
    "in a large mixing bowl, combine eggplant, preserved lemon, olive oil, black peppercorns, salt, paprika, cumin, and cayenne pepper.",
    "mix well until eggplant is evenly coated.",
    "spread the mixture in a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "bake for 30 minutes.",
    "remove from the oven and mix in tomato paste and water.",
    "return to the oven and bake for an additional 15 minutes.",
    "remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes.",
    "serve warm, topped with feta cheese if desired.",
    "repeat as necessary to accelerate recovery."
  ],
